    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SAVED 是一款第一人称氛围恐怖游戏，故事发生在废弃的房屋和阴森的豪宅中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索黑暗的房间和狭窄的走廊，与僵尸战斗，寻找武器，并利用光源生存。解开谜题，寻找钥匙，打开上锁的门，进入房屋的新区域。危险潜伏在每一扇门后，寂静并不可靠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个决定都要付出代价。<br>房子在注视着你，也许根本没有逃生之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
